sentences: Rock N Roll Hi Fives are a rock and roll four-piece from New Jersey, that formed in 2013.
J. Centeno performed in the late 1990s band Plug Spark Sanjay and the post-millennial band American Watercolor Movement.
Centeno and G. Centeno began playing music around 2010, and Ev.
The band cites musical influence from AC/DC, Nirvana, Teenage Fanclub, Pavement and early Rolling Stones, as well as '90s indie rock.
Rock N Roll Hi Fives' debut EP, Make it Happen, was released on 15 December 2014.
Rock N Roll Hi Fives' second EP, Gold Glitter Shoes, was released on 16 June 2015.
They made their first tour of the United States in 2015.
Rock N Roll Hi Fives performed at the North Jersey Indie Rock Festival on 23 September 2017.
Hi Fives released their third EP The Beat the Sound the Dragon's Roar with them, on 21 October 2017.
In 2018, Rock N Roll Hi Fives went on a six-show tour of Japan, and published a tour journal in Jersey Beat.
Re-introducing the RocknRoll Hi-Fives, their ten-track debut album, released on 29 June 2018.
